614
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:58,700
♫ <i>You are my daylight, the love of my life</i> ♫

615
00:41:58,700 --> 00:42:06,140
♫ <i>時が経ってもそこにいる</i> ♫

616
00:42:17,340 --> 00:42:18,640
ソンさん

